snippet.title: Wasco Unit-42 - Pre-launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Wasco is a dystopic sci-fi short role-playing game developed by Gray Lake Studios.

Visit http://www.wascogame.com for more information on the game.

The track bit used in this video for this game is used with permission from artist Judson Cowan. The song is called "A Repeated History" and can be found in the "Technology Crisis II" album.

Visit http://www.tettix.net/ for more information on the artist.
